ZH: 我家有三层房子。
EN: My house has three floors.

ZH: 我房子的装修很漂亮。
EN: The interior design of my house is beautiful.

ZH: 我的房子有一个大花园。
EN: My house has a big garden.

ZH: 房子里有很多家具。
EN: There are a lot of furniture in the house.

ZH: 我的房子离学校很近。
EN: My house is very close to the school.

ZH: 每个夜晚，我躺在房子的床上。
EN: Every night, I lie on the bed in the house.

ZH: 我一直梦想有一个自己的房子。
EN: I have always dreamed of having my own house.

ZH: 我和我的家人共同生活在这个房子里。
EN: My family and I live together in this house.

ZH: 她的房子很大，可以容纳很多人。
EN: Her house is big enough to accommodate a lot of people.

ZH: 这栋房子是一个建筑师设计的。
EN: This house was designed by an architect.

ZH: 她在这个房子里长大了。
EN: She grew up in this house.

ZH: 这个房子的门锁坏了。
EN: The lock on the door of this house is broken.

ZH: 这座城市有很多古老的房子。
EN: This city has many old houses.

ZH: 我的房子靠近海边。
EN: My house is close to the seaside.

ZH: 这幢房子的外观很奇特。
EN: The exterior of this building is very unique.

ZH: 我朋友的房子有一个游泳池。
EN: My friend's house has a swimming pool.

ZH: 这个房子年久失修，需要进行翻新。
EN: This house is in disrepair and needs renovation.

ZH: 这栋房子有一个宽敞的客厅。
EN: This house has a spacious living room.

ZH: 爷爷的房子建在山上，风景很美。
EN: Grandpa's house is built on the mountain, and the view is beautiful.

ZH: 我的房子有阳台，可以晒太阳。
EN: My house has a balcony where I can sunbathe.
